h cases</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. σχῆμα</foreign>, when several cases of the same Noun follow one another, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4013.tlg003:359:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Simp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ in Cat.\">in Cat.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">359.9</biblScope></bibl>. <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">-κῶς, ἀντωνυμίαι κάτωθεν μὲν π. κινοῦνται ἄνωθεν δὲ προσωπικῶς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4093.tlg001:2:418\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Choerob.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">in Theod.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.418</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> H. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n91283.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> Math., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πτωτικόν, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen></foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">special case</tr_> of a problem, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2032.tlg001:850:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Papp.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">850.19</biblScope></bibl>, al.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}